{"tid":500900,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)Prison Break逃 第5季","createTime":"2017-12-16T09:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T18:44:45.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"046800bfd5928ca7ba53e795ab7e561201fdfece","tid":500900,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=73373061\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e5087df8\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=88336665\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/17/14/768x959/gallery-1491316890-pb-sc71-0174-hires1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F17%2F14%2F768x959%2Fgallery-1491316890-pb-sc71-0174-hires1.jpg&h=5e2f8011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由茶包哥（羅伯特&middot;克耐普飾）提供的一條消息，林肯（多米尼克&middot;珀塞爾飾）和莎拉（莎拉&middot;韋恩&middot;卡麗絲飾）發現邁克爾（文特沃斯&middot;米勒飾）實際上還活著，並且被ISIL關在了也門的叫做奧傑吉亞的監獄中。之後他們開始計劃著不僅要幫邁克爾越獄，還要幫他逃出也門這個國家，並一起將幕後操控一切的波塞冬（馬克&middot;費厄斯坦飾）繩之以法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=96e67d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=20df07d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bbcc2f7fe8858f23c451238421183d1884c3a9","tid":500900,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5708ff3cf64780ebd9a281342b1de1e35d3570","tid":500900,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06224b95d7cb0fa3fabcbc434d14c30b07a6e246","tid":500900,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf5248b5a55acf3cd1c0d1d23eda437dbfcf58b","tid":500900,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12